<h2 id="resumen">Resumen</h2>

<h3 id="cu√°les-son-los-usos-comunes-de-gee">¬øCu√°les son los usos comunes de GEE?</h3>

<ul>
  <li>operate on petabytes of imagery using Google‚Äôs cloud</li>
  <li>embed outputs in apps</li>
  <li>store, share and version control your code</li>
  <li>import and export your own raster and vector data (assets)</li>
  <li>share your own raster and vector data</li>
  <li>export your analysis</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="para-qu√©-no-ha-sido-dise√±ado-gee">¬øPara qu√© no ha sido dise√±ado GEE?</h3>

<ul>
  <li>cartography</li>
  <li>heavy duty vector operations</li>
  <li>DIY parallelization. As stated in Gorelick et al. 2017, ‚ÄúThe price of liberation from these details [of parallelization] is that the user is unable to influence them.‚Äù</li>
</ul>
